Text: These should really be Other.  They are not audiobooks, but rather pdf's.

Thank you W55. Obviously a great deal of work went into this project and I for one appreciated very much.

Perhaps a better category choice might have been made but I never look into Other so I would've missed out.

Thank you again and best wishes for the New Year.
Really nice collection. Thanks for the effort! I needed quite a few of these. Happy New Year and thanks again
